transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan ji sir, main keh rahi thi ki ye aap waha pe unmute karenge na sir, unmute option aapko diya gaya hua hai, aapki aawaz nahi aa rahi thi sir.
Customer: Kya kya option diya gaya hai?
Executive: Ek baar aap join karo na sir Google Meet pe bata deti hu aapko.
Customer: Matlab Google Meet mein main join kar raha hu, theek hai? Lekin kya link bhi hai?
Executive: Haan haan haan, waha pe jo mic ka option rehta hai na sir, mic ka option. Theek hai? Mic ka jo option diya rehta hai na mic wala.
Customer: Achha.
Executive: Haan haan haan, ek baar join karke aap mic pe click karoge na toh automatically sir na aap bol paoge toh aapki aawaz mere tak pahunch payegi sir.
Customer: Aawaz nahi jayega, main toh desktop se kar raha hu na.
Executive: Achha desktop se aap kar rahe ho? Theek hai sir, ek minute. Ji.
Customer: Toh join now kar raha hu.
Executive: Haan sir, aap join karo sir, join karegi aap.
Hmm.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer's voice not audible to the executive.



Resolution:

- Executive guided the customer to unmute on Google Meet.



Next Steps: 

- None



Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral
